room_title: Escape room "Wonderland" by Symbology Escape Rooms in San Jose
room_description: You have returned from Wonderland and told your fantastic tales of adventure. You are accused of delusions and trapped in a psychiatrist's office while he calls the institution to take you away. The only way to avoid capture is to escape the room. Can you descend into madness and return to Wonderland before you are locked away for good?
